{"tid":1639272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"熱血時報記者被玻璃樽擊中送院　中大學生報落井下石","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:29:33.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"507f7302da3dd71c15e2acc96cfed69a1c7fe132","tid":1639272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-08-2019/56578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-08-2019%2F56578&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=79749b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-08-2019/56578</a><br />\n<br />\n本台記者於周一（10月7日）晚上11時許，於彌敦道旺角彌敦道振宜大廈對開採訪期間，被高處擲下的玻璃樽擊中，隨即頭破血流，已送院治理，現時清醒。 事件發生之後，多個主流媒體，包括香港電台、商業電台等都有報道，可見記者受傷是一件十分嚴重事件，豈料中大學生報Facebook專頁直播期間，旁述居然對本台記者受傷落井下石。 當時有示威者正討論是否殺上振宜大廈時，中大學生報的記者開fb直播時指「如果啲人知道嗰個記者係《熱血時報》黃洋達派過嚟嘅呢，究竟呢會唔會仲幫佢報仇呢」、「網傳成日篤人灰嘅黃洋達、《熱血時報》嘅人嚟架」、「如果揼中《立場》，啲人殺咗上去片甲不留」。當時他回應一名叫「Wai Ho Lee」網民的留言，該留言指「知係熱狗應該會沖上去掉多幾件家私落黎再捉人」，他回應說「我唔可以咁講啦，我只能夠話有機會囉」。該條直播片段，於凌晨2時半被刪除。 本台記者是為了公義，為了真相而受傷，對於中大學生報旁述如此口不擇言，實在令人齒冷。 相關報道： 旺角採訪被高處擲下玻璃樽擊中 本台記者頭部受傷送院 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-07-2019/56573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-07-2019%2F56573&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=6b8a494d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-07-2019/56573</a><br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-08-2019/56578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F10-08-2019%2F56578&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vi3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=79749b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/10-08-2019/56578</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"718b55580fb120cb7e7336428f490523c8441a5c","tid":1639272,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d31991a582bf0c6702fe81972795d2571c6aea40","tid":1639272,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbb7075d7d4346d54303f6404b30bc2daea63b1","tid":1639272,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91318d698ae9a9a0d1ca6831cf1c8b75d0d5bc6a","tid":1639272,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"熱狗抵死 比藍絲打死都冇問題 我地連登仔會眾籌比替天行道既藍絲打官司<br />\nConnect🥰"},{"pid":"ce5b148a1a3cc7e52bb6f67d74a413bfcb55ebc3","tid":1639272,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91318d698ae9a9a0d1ca6831cf1c8b75d0d5bc6a","tid":1639272,"uid":131282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"熱狗抵死 比藍絲打死都冇問題 我地連登仔會眾籌比替天行道既藍絲打官司<br />\nConnect🥰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:26:33.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a7d25bbe255aa958aeb53347008519b68d2846e7","tid":1639272,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:28:28.000Z","msg":"中大呢次又有d on9"},{"pid":"e199b5e59c5be829d7427212a9686d23109c86de","tid":1639272,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:29:33.000Z","msg":"咪再玩分化"}]}